WEBVTT

01:53.200 --> 01:55.280
2007.

01:56.600 --> 01:59.000
1995.

02:00.320 --> 02:02.720
1991.

02:03.560 --> 02:05.680
This handsome man and beautiful woman in the photo

02:05.680 --> 02:07.480
are my and Mu Qingjun's parents.

02:08.080 --> 02:09.199
In today's words,

02:09.240 --> 02:11.800
they were best girlfriends and best bros.

02:11.960 --> 02:14.220
They even held their weddings together.

02:15.240 --> 02:16.700
Maybe it was to save money.

02:17.400 --> 02:18.440
Of course, this tacit understanding

02:18.440 --> 02:20.120
also extended to having children.

02:20.120 --> 02:21.680
Almost at the same time,

02:21.760 --> 02:24.240
Mutou and I were born.

02:25.600 --> 02:26.440
You got it wrong.

02:26.440 --> 02:27.440
That's not me.

02:27.720 --> 02:29.560
The ugly one must be Mutou.

02:29.960 --> 02:33.160
His mischievousness has been like this since childhood.

02:34.560 --> 02:36.000
This one is me.

02:36.160 --> 02:36.720
How is it?

02:36.920 --> 02:39.240
Aren't I pretty and cute?

02:40.040 --> 02:41.120
But later,

02:41.280 --> 02:42.680
when I was five,

02:42.920 --> 02:45.280
fate played a big joke on me.

02:51.040 --> 02:52.120
Dabai.

02:52.560 --> 02:53.440
Tiejun.

02:53.920 --> 02:57.280
Take good care of my mom and Yuanbao.

02:58.720 --> 03:00.240
About today's accident,

03:01.360 --> 03:04.040
don't tell the kids.

03:04.360 --> 03:07.560
Tiejun, hang in there. Hang in there!

03:11.560 --> 03:13.120
Doctor! Doctor!

03:45.480 --> 03:47.640
Mom and Dad, rest in peace.

03:47.680 --> 03:49.640
I will take good care of Grandma.

03:53.880 --> 03:56.320
You don't have a father or a mother.

03:56.480 --> 03:58.960
A wild kid with no father and no mother.

03:58.960 --> 04:01.040
You have no father and no mother.

04:01.080 --> 04:02.800
A wild kid with no parents.

04:02.840 --> 04:05.360
Yuanbao, don't be afraid. I'm here.

04:06.080 --> 04:08.680
I will never forget him that afternoon.

04:09.520 --> 04:11.680
Mutou was like the Joker stepping on colorful auspicious clouds

04:11.680 --> 04:13.440
to save me.

04:15.760 --> 04:18.000
Yuanbao, don't be afraid.

04:18.240 --> 04:20.200
I will protect you from now on.

04:20.560 --> 04:23.800
You are not a wild kid without parents.

04:24.280 --> 04:26.160
We are a family.

04:28.440 --> 04:29.920
Yuanbao, don't cry.

04:30.000 --> 04:31.660
When you cry, I want to cry too.

04:36.480 --> 04:37.760
Grandma, wash your feet.

04:37.760 --> 04:38.760
Just like that,

04:39.000 --> 04:39.920
my childhood

04:40.000 --> 04:41.530
slowly began to have color.

04:42.280 --> 04:44.320
Here is a cute and charming grandma.

04:44.640 --> 04:46.640
Uncle and aunt who are like parents.

04:47.159 --> 04:48.040
And.

04:48.080 --> 04:49.880
Mutou, who always believed that one day

04:49.880 --> 04:51.720
he would obtain a martial arts manual

04:51.720 --> 04:54.120
and become a peerless master.

04:54.960 --> 04:56.800
Right, not Mutou.

04:58.320 --> 05:01.520
I am Huang Feihong from Foshan.

05:04.880 --> 05:06.840
Mutou, where is Foshan?

05:07.040 --> 05:09.560
Where did Sun Wukong and Tang Seng go to get the scriptures?

05:09.560 --> 05:11.800
They went to the West to get the scriptures.

05:11.800 --> 05:14.080
Right, Foshan.

05:14.080 --> 05:16.040
It must be in the West.

05:17.000 --> 05:19.060
Makes sense, you are amazing, Mutou.

05:19.520 --> 05:21.920
My son, how could you leave earlier than your mother?

05:21.920 --> 05:22.880
Of course.

05:22.960 --> 05:24.960
When we were kids, Mutou and I

05:24.960 --> 05:27.090
got into a lot of ridiculous mischief.

05:27.120 --> 05:29.360
Or I would cause trouble myself.

05:30.040 --> 05:30.720
But every time,

05:30.720 --> 05:32.120
Mutou would take the fall for me.

05:32.120 --> 05:33.200
I heard my mom say

05:33.240 --> 05:36.240
that TV shows are all made up by writers and directors.

05:36.400 --> 05:38.000
Then why don't they make up

05:38.240 --> 05:40.200
stories that make Grandma happy?

05:40.280 --> 05:42.840
They must all be crazy.

05:43.000 --> 05:44.120
Then can I be a screenwriter

05:44.120 --> 05:46.280
who doesn't go crazy?

05:46.360 --> 05:47.320
Yes.

05:52.960 --> 05:54.240
Who watered this?

05:55.640 --> 05:56.920
You watered it, didn't you?

05:56.920 --> 05:58.080
I watered it.

05:59.240 --> 06:00.600
Mom, I watered it.

06:00.680 --> 06:02.540
It has nothing to do with Yuanbao.

06:02.880 --> 06:03.920
That's enough.

06:04.000 --> 06:06.000
You've learned to cover for each other, huh?

06:06.000 --> 06:07.860
No one gets to watch TV from now on.

06:09.520 --> 06:12.960
Gentlemen passing by, please hear my words.

06:13.040 --> 06:17.680
Whoever travels to Nanjing,

06:17.800 --> 06:21.080
please deliver a message to my Sanlang.

06:21.160 --> 06:23.280
Even if Su San loses her life,

06:23.360 --> 06:30.760
I will repay you in the next life.

06:30.920 --> 06:32.180
Did Grandma sing well?

06:36.360 --> 06:38.080
With such wonderful people around me,

06:38.080 --> 06:39.200
I've also started to realize

06:39.200 --> 06:40.330
that I must stand up.

06:40.400 --> 06:41.680
I need to become stronger.

06:41.680 --> 06:43.200
I cannot be a burden to them.

06:43.200 --> 06:45.840
And we can't cause trouble for Mr. and Mrs. Mu.

06:46.280 --> 06:50.560
2006.

07:17.440 --> 07:19.370
Listen to me, you guys from Yuhong.

07:19.640 --> 07:20.840
If I see you

07:20.880 --> 07:23.400
stealing money from Zhicheng students again,

07:23.400 --> 07:25.400
don't blame me for showing no mercy.

07:35.159 --> 07:35.880
Kid,

07:38.960 --> 07:40.960
leave your name if you have the guts.

07:45.480 --> 07:47.840
The top dog of Zhicheng, Mu Qingjun.

07:59.720 --> 08:01.840
The top dog of Zhicheng. What is this?

08:02.200 --> 08:03.920
To Brother Zhicheng.

08:04.200 --> 08:05.800
I think you're Zhicheng's idiot.

08:05.800 --> 08:07.640
You really need a good beating.

08:07.880 --> 08:08.320
I...

08:09.080 --> 08:09.800
Mom, I really don't know

08:09.800 --> 08:10.480
who gave me this book.

08:10.480 --> 08:12.320
You don't study hard all day.

08:12.360 --> 08:13.320
I really don't know.

08:13.320 --> 08:14.880
What kind of books are you reading?

08:14.880 --> 08:15.600
Grandma!

08:15.880 --> 08:16.240
Grandma!

08:16.240 --> 08:16.800
Stop right there!

08:16.800 --> 08:17.280
Grandma! Grandma!

08:17.280 --> 08:17.840
Help me! Help me!

08:17.840 --> 08:18.920
Stop right there! Come back!

08:18.920 --> 08:20.000
All right.

08:20.040 --> 08:21.000
It's early in the morning.

08:21.000 --> 08:22.240
Don't be angry with him.

08:22.240 --> 08:23.080
Grandma, look at him.

08:23.080 --> 08:23.800
What kind of book is this?

08:23.800 --> 08:24.760
It's not mine.

08:24.920 --> 08:25.840
If it's not yours, whose is it?

08:25.840 --> 08:27.240
It's quite nice.

08:27.320 --> 08:29.050
I was like this when I was young.

08:29.640 --> 08:30.840
Grandma, don't spoil him.

08:30.840 --> 08:32.320
All right, come here.

08:32.360 --> 08:33.760
Scolded again?

08:34.679 --> 08:35.559
I have to beat you today.

08:35.559 --> 08:36.200
Come.

08:36.440 --> 08:37.039
Come here!

08:37.039 --> 08:37.799
Calm down.

08:38.200 --> 08:38.679
Come.

08:38.760 --> 08:39.440
Come here!

08:39.480 --> 08:40.039
Come, calm down.

08:40.039 --> 08:41.240
Auntie! Auntie! We're on your side.

08:41.240 --> 08:42.600
Watch me beat you today.

08:42.840 --> 08:44.240
Don't hurt the innocent!

08:45.080 --> 08:46.080
Stop right there!

08:46.880 --> 08:48.320
What's on your pants?

08:48.560 --> 08:49.480
Why are they so dirty?

08:49.480 --> 08:51.140
Did you get into a fight again?

08:51.160 --> 08:52.560
No, why would I fight?

08:52.600 --> 08:53.280
I didn't.

08:53.360 --> 08:55.160
Sit there and take it off.

08:55.400 --> 08:57.730
How can you go to school dressed like this?

08:58.960 --> 09:00.490
You really worry me all day.

09:00.640 --> 09:01.360
Get up.

09:04.160 --> 09:05.160
This kid.

09:06.160 --> 09:07.040
Funny, right?

09:07.360 --> 09:09.090
Just eat your food, little bun.

09:10.480 --> 09:11.600
Who's using the bathroom?

09:11.600 --> 09:12.320
Me.

09:20.240 --> 09:21.840
Me first. Me first.

09:24.760 --> 09:25.720
Ladies first.

09:30.200 --> 09:32.660
I think modern society needs to care for men.

09:35.080 --> 09:36.400
We have a bathroom at our place too.

09:36.400 --> 09:37.440
I'll go back to our place.

09:37.440 --> 09:38.640
You are already here.

09:38.960 --> 09:39.960
Just go in.

09:40.160 --> 09:41.480
Mu Qingjun.

09:42.040 --> 09:43.120
Mu Qingjun.

09:43.560 --> 09:46.480
Contemporary society really should care for men.

09:51.440 --> 09:52.080
Of course,

09:53.000 --> 09:54.330
women need it even more.

09:55.360 --> 09:56.920
Delivery. Delivery.

09:56.960 --> 09:58.420
Delivery for 'Cool Bear'.

09:59.280 --> 10:00.740
You went to the wrong door.

10:01.840 --> 10:03.120
Me.

10:04.480 --> 10:05.840
What 'Cool Bear'?

10:05.960 --> 10:07.040
I was totally confused.

10:07.040 --> 10:08.080
I'm going to see Han Han.

10:08.080 --> 10:09.920
I'm going to Shanghai, Grandma.

10:12.600 --> 10:14.840
Where is she going?

10:15.920 --> 10:17.280
Who is Han Han?

10:17.680 --> 10:19.040
The guy who failed exams

10:19.320 --> 10:21.780
and always wanted to drop out of high school.

10:22.680 --> 10:23.880
Not as handsome as me.

10:25.320 --> 10:26.560
Slow down.

10:27.200 --> 10:28.480
High school dropout?

10:29.400 --> 10:30.720
And failing exams?

11:03.720 --> 11:05.600
Look at my damn charm.

11:09.680 --> 11:12.600
Yes, really charming.

11:13.880 --> 11:15.200
Hearing your words,

11:15.720 --> 11:18.120
why do I suddenly feel a chill down my spine?

11:18.240 --> 11:20.900
Actually, there's something I want to tell you.

11:23.520 --> 11:24.080
Morning, Brother Qingyun.

11:24.080 --> 11:25.680
Tong Ruirui, my best friend.

11:26.080 --> 11:28.120
A cute and bright girl.

11:28.440 --> 11:30.080
A typical Pisces.

11:30.240 --> 11:32.160
Full of pink bubbles in her head.

11:32.760 --> 11:35.160
Don't be fooled by her cute and funny appearance,

11:35.160 --> 11:37.280
she's actually quite wild inside.

11:41.280 --> 11:42.240
Yuanbao.

11:43.320 --> 11:45.120
You really grant every request.

11:45.400 --> 11:46.840
How did you get this back?

11:47.480 --> 11:49.280
Thanks to your Brother Qingyun.

11:49.880 --> 11:52.680
The top guy in Zhicheng truly lives up to his reputation.

11:52.680 --> 11:54.120
With Brother Qingyun around,

11:54.120 --> 11:56.320
we all feel much safer.

11:57.120 --> 11:58.080
Piece of cake.

11:58.800 --> 12:00.360
Who could stop me?

12:00.400 --> 12:01.920
I can stop you.

12:02.800 --> 12:03.720
Shang Ningyu.

12:03.960 --> 12:05.800
In the realm of being goofy and cheeky,

12:05.800 --> 12:07.120
if he claims to be second,

12:07.120 --> 12:09.560
absolutely no one in the class would dare claim to be first.

12:09.560 --> 12:11.120
Born tone-deaf,

12:11.240 --> 12:13.560
his dream is to become the next Li Yuchun.

12:13.880 --> 12:15.160
To this day, I still don't know

12:15.160 --> 12:17.690
why he makes things so difficult for himself.

12:19.440 --> 12:20.840
That book from last time,

12:20.840 --> 12:23.040
you were the one who put it in my bag, right?

12:23.040 --> 12:24.920
My mom found it.

12:25.720 --> 12:27.680
Are you digging your own grave

12:27.760 --> 12:29.220
and just asking for death?

12:29.280 --> 12:31.480
Bro, I was just trying to show my respect

12:31.560 --> 12:32.890
and give you a surprise.

12:33.960 --> 12:35.000
I'm not interested.

12:35.000 --> 12:36.280
My mother's maiden home

12:36.280 --> 12:38.200
was outside Deshengmen in Beiping,

12:38.200 --> 12:39.320
outside Tucheng,

12:39.440 --> 12:41.760
in a small village on the main road to Dazhong Temple.

12:41.760 --> 12:42.880
Xing Yaqi.

12:43.360 --> 12:45.480
Our class monitor and class beauty.

12:45.880 --> 12:48.240
She is pretty, sings sweetly, and studies well.

12:48.240 --> 12:51.000
I wish I could be like her.

12:52.280 --> 12:54.410
Wang Zhiyong, the PE representative.

12:54.640 --> 12:56.200
All brawn and no brains.

12:56.520 --> 12:57.920
It is not very developed.

12:58.160 --> 13:01.280
Great, so beautiful.

13:02.040 --> 13:03.240
This is Zhang Dongbo.

13:03.880 --> 13:05.400
He claims to be a master diviner,

13:05.400 --> 13:07.560
well-versed in the Book of Changes and Bagua.

13:07.560 --> 13:08.160
By the way,

13:08.480 --> 13:10.340
I haven't introduced myself yet.

13:10.360 --> 13:12.800
I am the invincible, hardworking and motivated

13:12.800 --> 13:14.320
Xiong Yuanbao.

13:15.160 --> 13:16.480
But no matter how hard I try,

13:16.480 --> 13:18.140
my grades just won't improve.

13:19.200 --> 13:21.160
New Concept Writing Competition Semi-final Notice.

13:21.160 --> 13:22.720
This is probably

13:23.040 --> 13:25.170
my biggest achievement at this stage.

13:25.800 --> 13:27.080
Oh my god, Yuanbao!

13:27.160 --> 13:28.600
Is this the competition

13:28.640 --> 13:29.920
that Han Han and Guo Jingming participated in?

13:29.920 --> 13:30.800
Who is talking?

13:31.920 --> 13:34.450
Mr., we're going to have a writer in our class!

13:37.440 --> 13:38.560
Not bad, Yuanbao.

13:38.680 --> 13:39.680
But during class,

13:39.720 --> 13:41.760
don't discuss things unrelated to the class.

13:41.760 --> 13:42.840
Talk about it later.

13:42.840 --> 13:43.960
By the way, Yuanbao,

13:43.960 --> 13:45.400
you're the only one who hasn't submitted

13:45.400 --> 13:46.600
the essay about mother.

13:46.600 --> 13:48.530
Remember to hand it to me tomorrow.

13:53.080 --> 13:54.720
Okay, class is over.

13:54.840 --> 13:55.720
Stand up.

13:56.040 --> 13:59.040
Goodbye, Mr.

13:59.160 --> 14:00.200
Goodbye, class.

14:02.120 --> 14:03.800
Everyone.

14:03.880 --> 14:06.480
Yuanbao is playing the fool to catch the tiger.

14:06.480 --> 14:08.340
He's already in the semi-finals.

14:08.480 --> 14:09.960
Yuanbao, what did you write in your essay?

14:09.960 --> 14:11.200
If you really meet Han Han,

14:11.200 --> 14:12.560
get me an autograph.

14:12.680 --> 14:13.840
Get one for me too.

14:13.960 --> 14:14.640
No problem.

14:14.760 --> 14:16.640
If I can really meet him.

14:17.560 --> 14:18.520
But my friend,

14:18.640 --> 14:21.520
I see you're looking flushed recently.

14:21.600 --> 14:24.920
I'm afraid there will be unforeseen events on your trip.

14:25.240 --> 14:26.680
You jinx.

14:27.360 --> 14:28.280
Yuanbao,

14:28.560 --> 14:30.240
let me interview you

14:30.320 --> 14:31.920
about how you feel right now.

14:32.320 --> 14:33.240
Xiong Yuanbao.

14:33.960 --> 14:35.280
62.

14:36.120 --> 14:37.640
Your score is a joke.

14:39.200 --> 14:41.560
Why did you read it so loudly?

14:41.720 --> 14:42.960
Am I wrong?

14:43.120 --> 14:44.320
You didn't submit the essay,

14:44.320 --> 14:45.720
and you almost failed.

14:45.800 --> 14:46.840
You study here every day,

14:46.840 --> 14:48.480
but I don't know what you're actually learning.

14:48.480 --> 14:49.920
You're just putting on a show.

14:49.920 --> 14:51.580
You got the semifinal notice.

14:51.640 --> 14:52.840
Is that a big deal?

14:53.880 --> 14:54.810
What did you say?

14:56.880 --> 14:57.940
What are you doing?

14:58.520 --> 15:00.050
Are you trying to hit a girl?

15:07.080 --> 15:09.320
Mu Qingyun, what are you doing?

15:14.160 --> 15:16.160
A real man doesn't fight with girls.

15:18.000 --> 15:20.200
Look at your hair.

15:20.320 --> 15:21.760
And you have the nerve to argue with a girl?

15:21.760 --> 15:22.690
I'm telling you,

15:22.760 --> 15:24.120
get a haircut tomorrow.

15:24.440 --> 15:25.640
Instant karma.

15:26.520 --> 15:27.320
Students,

15:28.040 --> 15:29.320
don't learn from him.

15:29.760 --> 15:32.220
All right, pack your things. School's over.

15:45.160 --> 15:46.520
Don't just think about studying.

15:46.520 --> 15:48.560
Play a game and balance work and rest.

15:48.560 --> 15:49.400
I won't play.

15:49.640 --> 15:50.700
If you dare to play,

15:50.920 --> 15:52.560
let's see if Auntie doesn't punish you when she gets back.

15:52.560 --> 15:54.120
If I wasn't completely sure,

15:54.120 --> 15:55.450
how would I dare to play?

15:55.560 --> 15:56.960
If my mom catches me,

15:57.400 --> 15:58.960
she will definitely use lynching

15:58.960 --> 16:00.240
and skin me alive.

16:00.400 --> 16:02.120
I really suspect that we were

16:02.160 --> 16:03.320
switched at the hospital when we were little.

16:03.320 --> 16:04.400
My mom is your mom,

16:04.520 --> 16:05.680
and your mom is my...

16:09.360 --> 16:10.360
Sorry.

16:10.920 --> 16:12.640
I didn't mean to say that.

16:13.960 --> 16:16.160
It's fine. I'll play with you for a bit.

16:16.600 --> 16:17.800
But let's make a deal,

16:17.800 --> 16:20.000
don't get angry while playing the game.

16:20.000 --> 16:20.960
Absolutely.

16:21.040 --> 16:22.480
Why get angry over a game?

16:22.560 --> 16:23.240
Go, go, go.

16:25.280 --> 16:26.540
We lost because of you.

16:26.560 --> 16:27.840
Were you playing with your feet?

16:27.840 --> 16:29.560
I told you not to get angry over a game.

16:29.560 --> 16:30.840
Plus, I'm a girl.

16:30.880 --> 16:31.920
Who's angry?

16:31.960 --> 16:33.400
Isn't it your fault? Tell me.

16:33.400 --> 16:35.600
Mu Qingjun, you're still talking.

16:37.320 --> 16:38.600
Who started it?

16:39.640 --> 16:40.480
Him. Her.

16:41.760 --> 16:43.290
Bring out the family rules.

16:45.560 --> 16:47.080
Grandma. Grandma.

16:47.200 --> 16:48.840
Don't look at Grandma. Look at me.

16:48.840 --> 16:49.720
Let's begin.

17:05.599 --> 17:06.440
I've told you so many times

17:06.440 --> 17:08.170
not to fight, but you still did.

17:08.640 --> 17:09.839
How old are you?

17:10.480 --> 17:11.319
Apologize.

17:12.079 --> 17:13.280
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

17:13.800 --> 17:15.599
What are you waiting for? Start.

17:16.920 --> 17:20.440
Because we are a family,

17:20.760 --> 17:23.839
a family that loves each other.

17:24.400 --> 17:26.079
Fate brought us together.

17:26.160 --> 17:27.880
Only with heart can we cherish.

17:27.880 --> 17:31.040
Why let the dark clouds cover our eyes?

17:31.680 --> 17:33.240
The results are out, right?

17:33.880 --> 17:36.160
Yuanbao, 82 points.

17:36.200 --> 17:37.200
Not bad at all.

17:37.320 --> 17:39.250
Qingyun, where is your test paper?

17:40.320 --> 17:41.560
Take it out.

17:46.560 --> 17:47.960
Hurry up. Stop dawdling.

17:58.560 --> 18:00.200
Forty-eight?

18:02.080 --> 18:02.840
Look at you.

18:02.920 --> 18:05.200
You still have the nerve to play games with such low marks.

18:05.200 --> 18:06.720
Your hair is so long, and you haven't cut it.

18:06.720 --> 18:08.040
Your teacher already complained to me.

18:08.040 --> 18:09.370
Get a haircut right now.

18:09.920 --> 18:11.120
I got it.

18:11.240 --> 18:12.440
I won't play anymore.

18:12.640 --> 18:13.760
I'll study hard.

18:13.880 --> 18:14.920
Study hard.

18:15.080 --> 18:16.600
You used to have good grades when you were little.

18:16.600 --> 18:17.600
Look at you now.

18:17.720 --> 18:19.480
Have you ever scored higher than Yuanbao?

18:19.480 --> 18:21.360
Do you think you are the Chinese national football team?

18:21.360 --> 18:23.400
Consistently bad, aren't you? All day long...

18:23.400 --> 18:24.660
I'll beat you to death.

18:31.480 --> 18:32.280
Yuanbao,

18:32.440 --> 18:34.240
your homeroom teacher called me

18:37.520 --> 18:40.380
and said this essay competition is very important.

18:40.480 --> 18:43.040
She also praised your talent for writing.

18:46.920 --> 18:47.920
It scared me.

18:48.120 --> 18:50.380
I thought you two got into trouble again.

18:50.400 --> 18:51.160
Yuanbao,

18:51.240 --> 18:53.280
when are you going to the competition?

18:53.280 --> 18:54.200
This Saturday.

18:54.320 --> 18:55.180
This Saturday?

18:55.560 --> 18:56.420
That's so soon.

18:58.320 --> 19:00.760
I have an event at the factory on Saturday.

19:01.480 --> 19:02.940
Let your uncle go with you.

19:03.040 --> 19:05.720
I... I have a job interview.

19:08.160 --> 19:10.200
Dad, you're going to a job interview?

19:10.200 --> 19:11.440
No, no, no.

19:11.720 --> 19:13.650
It's another better opportunity.

19:13.880 --> 19:15.360
They insisted I go check it out

19:15.360 --> 19:16.960
and give them some guidance.

19:17.040 --> 19:19.480
It's fine. I'll go with Yuanbao.

19:19.600 --> 19:20.880
Don't worry.

19:21.440 --> 19:23.600
Grandma, I can go by myself.

19:23.840 --> 19:25.280
Big cities are very safe.

19:25.960 --> 19:27.640
With your IQ,

19:28.160 --> 19:29.560
if you go out alone...

19:30.440 --> 19:30.880
You!

19:31.440 --> 19:33.320
How dare you mock my IQ.

19:35.320 --> 19:36.400
These two kids.

19:37.160 --> 19:38.440
If she goes out alone,

19:38.840 --> 19:42.100
she'd probably help count the money if she gets kidnapped.

19:42.360 --> 19:44.640
How about this? Let Qingjun go with Yuanbao.

19:44.640 --> 19:45.760
They are grown up now.

19:45.760 --> 19:47.080
It's time for them to get some experience.

19:47.080 --> 19:47.680
Yes, get some experience.

19:47.680 --> 19:48.840
That works.

19:48.960 --> 19:50.480
They can keep each other company

19:50.480 --> 19:51.940
and look after each other.

19:51.960 --> 19:52.920
Us two?

19:53.120 --> 19:54.800
No looking after each other,

19:55.120 --> 19:56.720
and no mutual progress.

19:56.800 --> 19:58.120
Only mutual disgust.

19:58.280 --> 19:59.440
Mutual sarcasm.

20:01.720 --> 20:03.180
You two are so articulate.

20:03.720 --> 20:06.400
Alright, the Shanghai trip is settled.

20:06.800 --> 20:08.360
Qingjun, when you're away from home,

20:08.360 --> 20:09.820
take good care of Yuanbao.

20:10.680 --> 20:13.680
Mom, how much travel expenses

20:14.920 --> 20:16.360
are you going to give us?

20:19.120 --> 20:20.120
Five hundred.

20:20.200 --> 20:21.280
No more than that.

20:21.800 --> 20:24.660
Yuanbao, you manage the money. Don't give it to him.

20:25.440 --> 20:27.400
Mom, only five hundred?

20:27.720 --> 20:29.120
What can five hundred do?

20:29.200 --> 20:31.160
Travel expenses, accommodation...

20:31.160 --> 20:32.480
It'll all be gone.

20:33.240 --> 20:35.440
Besides, Yuanbao eats so much.

20:36.000 --> 20:37.600
I'm afraid she'll starve.

20:40.280 --> 20:41.840
Yuanbao, eat more meat.

20:53.280 --> 20:53.760
Aunt Ling.

20:53.760 --> 20:55.120
Yuanbao, studying?

21:04.880 --> 21:05.960
I have

21:06.160 --> 21:07.420
another 500 yuan here.

21:08.120 --> 21:09.280
Take it.

21:09.560 --> 21:11.360
Also, during dinner today,

21:11.480 --> 21:13.360
judging by your uncle's reaction,

21:13.360 --> 21:15.320
I think he might give you money too.

21:16.240 --> 21:18.000
If that's the case,

21:18.440 --> 21:19.520
I want to see

21:19.680 --> 21:20.720
how much secret money

21:20.720 --> 21:22.400
he has hidden from me.

21:23.200 --> 21:24.060
In this matter,

21:24.160 --> 21:25.640
you must take my side.

21:25.760 --> 21:26.720
Hear me?

21:31.120 --> 21:32.650
It's not easy being a woman.

21:39.520 --> 21:40.400
Who is it?

21:40.480 --> 21:42.440
Yuanbao, can I come in?

21:44.240 --> 21:47.240
Uncle, wait a second.

22:01.400 --> 22:03.320
Uncle, why are you here?

22:03.400 --> 22:04.200
Yuanbao, listen to me.

22:04.200 --> 22:05.760
Come in.

22:06.200 --> 22:07.120
Take a seat.

22:11.320 --> 22:12.320
Listen to me.

22:12.880 --> 22:13.920
While your aunt is

22:14.000 --> 22:15.200
out buying soy sauce,

22:15.280 --> 22:16.120
I brought you

22:17.400 --> 22:20.520
my secret savings.

22:20.880 --> 22:23.760
Remember to buy some good food on the road.

22:24.080 --> 22:25.280
Travel comfortably,

22:25.360 --> 22:26.560
and don't mistreat yourself.

22:26.560 --> 22:27.320
Hear me?

22:29.040 --> 22:30.640
What's wrong with your eyes?

22:31.440 --> 22:32.200
Take it.

22:32.480 --> 22:33.560
Here's 600.

22:33.840 --> 22:35.280
I saved it for months.

22:36.760 --> 22:39.240
Spend it wisely.

22:39.600 --> 22:40.600
If there's any left,

22:40.600 --> 22:42.260
remember to give it back to me.

22:43.200 --> 22:44.960
Don't tell your aunt.

22:45.480 --> 22:47.040
It's not easy being a man.

22:49.480 --> 22:51.140
What's wrong with your mouth?

22:54.400 --> 22:55.800
Your aunt must be back.

23:06.720 --> 23:07.720
Yuanbao.

23:10.440 --> 23:11.360
Honey.

23:12.680 --> 23:13.680
Everyone's here.

23:15.560 --> 23:16.690
Aunt Wenying, Aunt.

23:16.800 --> 23:18.520
You keep Yuanbao company.

23:18.760 --> 23:20.600
I'll go do some chores.

23:24.160 --> 23:25.280
Auntie, Uncle.

23:28.440 --> 23:29.600
What's going on?

23:31.000 --> 23:33.200
Let's go home. I'll deal with you later.

23:34.320 --> 23:35.560
Gently.

24:01.200 --> 24:03.930
This is the style Zhicheng's top guy should have.

24:04.240 --> 24:07.920
I am Mu of the Zang'ai Family.

24:14.680 --> 24:16.040
I'm going to school by myself today.

24:16.040 --> 24:17.440
Don't get too close to me.

24:26.000 --> 24:27.060
What is a disguise?

24:27.080 --> 24:28.200
This is a disguise.

24:28.720 --> 24:30.320
You can't even recognize me.

24:34.960 --> 24:35.840
Mutou.

24:39.280 --> 24:40.840
Come, solve this problem.

24:47.240 --> 24:48.760
Pass. Next.

24:49.200 --> 24:50.560
What do you mean 'pass'?

24:51.160 --> 24:52.440
Teacher, you forgot.

24:52.520 --> 24:53.480
You said before

24:53.560 --> 24:55.320
to quickly skip the questions we don't know

24:55.320 --> 24:56.800
to save everyone's time.

24:58.480 --> 25:00.000
Then there's nothing wrong with saying that.

25:00.000 --> 25:00.920
Yuanbao.

25:11.880 --> 25:14.480
Xiong Yuanbao is reading a leisure book in class.

25:14.480 --> 25:16.800
Sorry, teacher. I was wrong.

25:23.800 --> 25:24.920
Mr. Tian.

25:26.280 --> 25:29.520
It seems my class isn't attractive enough.

25:30.000 --> 25:31.800
Yuanbao finds it very boring.

25:32.000 --> 25:33.400
She shared this with me.

25:33.960 --> 25:35.490
Now I'm sharing it with you.

25:37.680 --> 25:38.600
Class dismissed.

25:38.600 --> 25:39.320
Stand up.

25:40.160 --> 25:43.600
Goodbye, teacher.

25:43.680 --> 25:44.740
Take care, Mr. Liu.

25:46.680 --> 25:47.540
Xiong Yuanbao,

25:48.200 --> 25:49.060
and Mu Qingjun,

25:50.200 --> 25:51.320
come to my office.

25:52.960 --> 25:54.960
Nothing good comes from arrogance.

25:55.080 --> 25:56.080
Fellow Daoist.

25:57.080 --> 25:58.000
Well.

25:58.320 --> 26:00.480
It bodes ill.

26:00.720 --> 26:02.400
It's fulfilled.

26:03.080 --> 26:03.960
Tough guy,

26:04.400 --> 26:05.000
take care.

26:05.480 --> 26:06.320
Director,

26:06.600 --> 26:07.520
this is Xiong Yuanbao, who entered

26:07.520 --> 26:09.640
the re-examination of the New Concept.

26:09.640 --> 26:11.960
This child is usually very hardworking

26:12.200 --> 26:13.800
and especially likes writing,

26:13.800 --> 26:18.160
particularly reading these world classics.

26:18.320 --> 26:19.240
Right?

26:21.280 --> 26:23.800
I do like reading world classics.

26:23.920 --> 26:26.080
The younger generation is truly formidable.

26:26.080 --> 26:27.280
Our Zhicheng School

26:27.520 --> 26:29.250
has always been top in science,

26:29.560 --> 26:31.760
but relatively weaker in liberal arts.

26:32.080 --> 26:33.480
A New Concept contestant

26:33.520 --> 26:34.840
is a first for us.

26:35.080 --> 26:38.080
You must win glory for the school this time.

26:39.080 --> 26:39.880
Mr. Tian,

26:40.040 --> 26:41.640
if there's any need for tutoring in composition,

26:41.640 --> 26:43.120
our school will fully support it.

26:43.120 --> 26:43.800
Okay, don't worry, Director.

26:43.800 --> 26:44.930
I'll leave you to it.

26:47.400 --> 26:48.200
Mr. Men.

26:48.640 --> 26:50.000
No, Mr. Tian.

26:50.680 --> 26:52.280
Then about my world classic,

26:52.880 --> 26:53.840
can I have it back?

26:53.840 --> 26:55.280
Don't even think about it.

26:55.280 --> 26:56.240
Xiong Yuanbao,

26:56.320 --> 26:58.850
Give you an inch and you take a mile, don't you?

26:59.040 --> 27:00.680
Did your parents send you to school

27:00.680 --> 27:02.120
just to read these...

27:02.240 --> 27:03.680
idle books?

27:04.200 --> 27:05.130
I'm telling you,

27:05.240 --> 27:07.640
focus on the competition and nothing else.

27:10.400 --> 27:11.240
And you,

27:11.520 --> 27:12.440
Mu Qingyun.

27:12.880 --> 27:14.240
What are you laughing at?

27:14.240 --> 27:15.570
You're only a freshman.

27:15.840 --> 27:17.280
Look at your hair.

27:17.360 --> 27:18.920
Do you think you're a hedgehog?

27:18.920 --> 27:19.920
By the way, Yuanbao.

27:19.920 --> 27:22.160
Since you made it to the New Concept Writing Competition semi-finals,

27:22.160 --> 27:23.640
about that essay about mothers,

27:23.640 --> 27:25.080
when are you going to hand it in?

27:25.080 --> 27:26.720
I've urged you several times.

27:26.720 --> 27:27.840
Everyone else has handed it in.

27:27.840 --> 27:29.640
I just urged you yesterday and you still haven't.

27:29.640 --> 27:31.240
Do you have a problem with me?

27:34.120 --> 27:35.120
Xiong Yuanbao,

27:35.600 --> 27:37.200
Have you learned from Mu Qingyun

27:37.200 --> 27:38.930
to always go against teachers?

27:40.880 --> 27:42.120
I don't know how to write it.

27:42.120 --> 27:44.520
Yuanbao, what are you talking about?

27:44.880 --> 27:46.140
What's wrong with you?

27:46.600 --> 27:48.530
Do you want me to call your parents?

27:52.280 --> 27:53.540
Don't call my parents.

27:54.600 --> 27:55.520
I'll write it.

27:57.200 --> 27:57.880
Yuanbao.

28:12.280 --> 28:13.400
What happened?

28:15.120 --> 28:15.920
Mu Qingjun.

28:17.200 --> 28:18.840
What's wrong with Xiong Yuanbao?

28:18.840 --> 28:20.280
No, I don't get it.

28:20.360 --> 28:22.760
It's just an essay. Is it really necessary?

28:23.080 --> 28:24.840
Don't you live opposite her house?

28:24.840 --> 28:25.720
Tell her

28:26.080 --> 28:27.610
I want to talk to her family.

28:30.080 --> 28:30.960
Mr. Tian.

28:33.160 --> 28:34.080
Yuanbao,

28:34.920 --> 28:36.080
she has her reasons.

28:41.880 --> 28:44.740
What's so great about getting a semi-final notice?

28:46.000 --> 28:47.040
Got scolded, huh?

29:08.040 --> 29:09.120
Did you know?

29:09.320 --> 29:11.380
Xiong Yuanbao is actually an orphan.

29:11.880 --> 29:12.960
An orphan?

29:13.800 --> 29:14.720
No way.

29:14.880 --> 29:15.680
It's true.

29:16.000 --> 29:19.060
I heard Mu Qingyun telling the teacher with my own ears.

29:19.080 --> 29:20.080
Did you know?

29:20.200 --> 29:21.240
Xiong Yuanbao's grandmother

29:21.240 --> 29:23.120
works as a nanny at Mu Qingyun's house.

29:23.120 --> 29:24.840
I heard she's making money for her

29:24.840 --> 29:26.500
to cover her living expenses.

29:27.360 --> 29:28.560
No way, Zhicheng.

29:28.560 --> 29:28.960
No way.

29:29.520 --> 29:31.120
I heard about this a long time ago.

29:31.120 --> 29:33.050
The fireworks factory explosion.

29:33.120 --> 29:35.360
It seems it was due to a mistake.

29:35.880 --> 29:36.800
I know.

29:36.880 --> 29:38.080
My mom mentioned this to me.

29:38.080 --> 29:40.280
I think Yuanbao's parents...

29:40.520 --> 29:41.800
I'll leave the factory to you.

29:41.800 --> 29:42.520
Okay.

29:45.760 --> 29:47.420
I never expected the culprits

29:47.520 --> 29:49.280
to be Xiong Yuanbao's parents.

29:51.480 --> 29:52.440
Mom.

29:53.040 --> 29:53.880
Yuanbao.

29:55.440 --> 29:56.600
Mom promises you,

29:56.720 --> 29:58.400
she'll be right back.

30:05.880 --> 30:06.880
Really?

30:08.680 --> 30:11.400
How many families did that ruin?

30:11.960 --> 30:13.800
And they ended up dying themselves.
